Interface Processor

  • All Superinterfaces:

    public interface Processor
extends Handler, Notifier<Handler>
    A Handler that pre-processes and post-processes received events, before notifying the next Handler.

    It can add validation, redirection, cancellation, or data enhancement capabilities.
